          "source_html": "<div class=\"big-section\"><div class=\"group-instruction\"><p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\"><strong>Questions 1 – 5</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1;\"><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">Complete the notes. Write <strong>ONE WORD ONLY</strong> in each gap.</p></div>\r\n            <div class=\"q-block normal-q\">\r\n                <div class=\"q-stem\">\r\n                    <span class=\"q-num\">1</span>\r\n                    <div class=\"q-text\"><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.5;\"><strong>History of farming</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\"><strong>Traditional thinking:</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">• </span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">farming developed due to food </span><strong><span class=\"input-blank\" data-question=\"q1\"></span></strong></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                \r\n                <button class=\"btn-toggle\">显示解析</button>\r\n                <div class=\"ans-box\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-row\"><strong>正确答案：</strong> <span class=\"ans-tag\">1</span> shortage</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"analysis\">\r\n                <div class=\"sub-analysis-item\">\r\n                    <div class=\"sa-title\">Question 1</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"sa-content\"><p>定位关键词：</p><p>Traditional thinking，due to</p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p>原文：</p><p>A段, “The traditional view of the history of farming is that it all began in response to the shortage of food for foraging and hunting in the dry conditions after the Ice Age about 8,000-10,000 years ago.”</p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p>解析：</p><p>原文提到在干旱的条件下，为了应对觅食和狩猎所需食物短缺，农业开始了。</p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p>同义词替换：</p><p>in response to=due to</p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div><div class=\"big-section\">\r\n            <div class=\"q-block normal-q\">\r\n                <div class=\"q-stem\">\r\n                    <span class=\"q-num\">2</span>\r\n                    <div class=\"q-text\"><p style=\"text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">•&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">farming started after a change in climatic&nbsp;</span><strong><span class=\"input-blank\" data-question=\"q2\"></span></strong></p><p style=\"text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1;\"><br/></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                \r\n                <button class=\"btn-toggle\">显示解析</button>\r\n                <div class=\"ans-box\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-row\"><strong>正确答案：</strong> <span class=\"ans-tag\">2</span> conditions</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"analysis\">\r\n                <div class=\"sub-analysis-item\">\r\n                    <div class=\"sa-title\">Question 2</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"sa-content\"><p>定位关键词：</p><p>farming started</p><p><br/></p><p>原文：</p><p>A段, “The traditional view of the history of farming is that it all began in response to the shortage of food for foraging and hunting in the dry conditions after the Ice Age about 8,000-10,000 years ago.”</p><p><br/></p><p>解析：</p><p>原文中提到传统观点认为农业起源于干旱条件下，觅食和狩猎食物不足</p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div><div class=\"big-section\">\r\n            <div class=\"q-block normal-q\">\r\n                <div class=\"q-stem\">\r\n                    <span class=\"q-num\">3</span>\r\n                    <div class=\"q-text\"><p style=\"text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.5;\"><strong>More recent findings:</strong></p><p style=\"text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">•&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">oldest evidences of arable farming found at a&nbsp;</span><strong><span class=\"input-blank\" data-question=\"q3\"></span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">&nbsp;in Israel where bread was made from</span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                \r\n                <button class=\"btn-toggle\">显示解析</button>\r\n                <div class=\"ans-box\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-row\"><strong>正确答案：</strong> <span class=\"ans-tag\">3</span> site</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"analysis\">\r\n                <div class=\"sub-analysis-item\">\r\n                    <div class=\"sa-title\">Question 3</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"sa-content\"><p>定位关键词：</p><p>Israel</p><p><br/></p><p>原文：</p><p>B段, “However, in 2005, researchers working near the Sea of Galilee in Israel discovered a site known as Ohalo Il. Here, at least 23,000 years ago, people used seeds of wild grasses such as emmer wheat and barley, and ground them into flour to make bread.”</p><p><br/></p><p>解析：</p><p>原文提到以色列加利利海附近工作的研究人员发现了一个被称为Ohalo Il的遗址，这里的人们用种子磨成面粉制作面包。</p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div><div class=\"big-section\">\r\n            <div class=\"q-block normal-q\">\r\n                <div class=\"q-stem\">\r\n                    <span class=\"q-num\">4</span>\r\n                    <div class=\"q-text\"><p style=\"text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">•&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">wild cereal plants like&nbsp;</span><strong><span class=\"input-blank\" data-question=\"q4\"></span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">&nbsp;and emmer wheat</span></p><p style=\"text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1;\"><br/></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                \r\n                <button class=\"btn-toggle\">显示解析</button>\r\n                <div class=\"ans-box\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-row\"><strong>正确答案：</strong> <span class=\"ans-tag\">4</span> barley</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"analysis\">\r\n                <div class=\"sub-analysis-item\">\r\n                    <div class=\"sa-title\">Question 4</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"sa-content\"><p>定位关键词：</p><p>emmer wheat</p><p><br/></p><p>原文：</p><p>B段, “However, in 2005, researchers working near the Sea of Galilee in Israel discovered a site known as Ohalo Il. Here, at least 23,000 years ago, people used seeds of wild grasses such as emmer wheat and barley, and ground them into flour to make bread.”</p><p><br/></p><p>解析：</p><p>原文提到提到2005年，在以色列加利利海附近的Ohalo II遗址，考古学家发现了一些距今至少23,000年前的人类活动痕迹。这些人类使用野生谷物种子，例如小麦和大麦，并将它们磨成面粉制作面包。</p><p><br/></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div><div class=\"big-section\">\r\n            <div class=\"q-block normal-q\">\r\n                <div class=\"q-stem\">\r\n                    <span class=\"q-num\">5</span>\r\n                    <div class=\"q-text\"><p style=\"text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.5;\"><strong>Gradual emergence of farming:</strong></p><p style=\"text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">•&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">people started to keep animals people began using seeds of wild grasses to grow crops</span></p><p style=\"text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.5;\"><strong>Some effects of early farming:</strong></p><p style=\"text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">•&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">people stopped&nbsp;</span><strong><span class=\"input-blank\" data-question=\"q5\"></span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">&nbsp;animals and picking wild plants to feed themselves</span></p><p style=\"text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">•&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">extra food made trading possible</span></p><p style=\"text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">•&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">as people settled, positive aspects of civilisation appeared</span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                \r\n                <button class=\"btn-toggle\">显示解析</button>\r\n                <div class=\"ans-box\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-row\"><strong>正确答案：</strong> <span class=\"ans-tag\">5</span> hunting</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"analysis\">\r\n                <div class=\"sub-analysis-item\">\r\n                    <div class=\"sa-title\">Question 5</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"sa-content\"><p>定位关键词：</p><p>picking wild plants</p><p><br/></p><p>原文：</p><p>D段, “When arable farming did start, the effect on the human way of life was dramatic. No longer did people have to move around hunting and foraging.”</p><p><br/></p><p>解析：</p><p>原文提到农业如何取代了狩猎。</p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div><div class=\"big-section\"><div class=\"group-instruction\"><p style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><strong>Questions 6 – 13</strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 1;\"><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">Choose <strong>TRUE </strong>if the statement agrees with the information given in the text, choose <strong>FALSE </strong>if the statement contradicts the information, or choose <strong>NOT GIVEN </strong>if there is no information on this.</p></div>\r\n            <div class=\"q-block normal-q\">\r\n                <div class=\"q-stem\">\r\n                    <span class=\"q-num\">6</span>\r\n                    <div class=\"q-text\"><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><strong>Jay Stock found that Egyptian hunter-gatherers were smaller than early Egyptian farmers.</strong></span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"opt-list\" style=\"margin:10px 0 10px 25px;\">\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_6\" id=\"opt_6_A\" data-zyz-question=\"q6\" value=\"A\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_6_A\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>A.</strong> TRUE</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_6\" id=\"opt_6_B\" data-zyz-question=\"q6\" value=\"B\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_6_B\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>B.</strong> FALSE</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_6\" id=\"opt_6_C\" data-zyz-question=\"q6\" value=\"C\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_6_C\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>C.</strong> NOT GIVEN</label>\r\n        </div></div>\r\n                <button class=\"btn-toggle\">显示解析</button>\r\n                <div class=\"ans-box\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-row\"><strong>正确答案：</strong> B. FALSE</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"analysis\"><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Q</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">6</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"> FALSE</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">定位关键词：</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">hunter-gatherers</p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">原文：</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">E段</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">, “</span>He made his damning comment after he studied the bones of hunter-gatherers living in Egypt just before farming developed and found that these people were significantly taller and healthier than the first farmers were.<span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">”</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"> </span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">解析：</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(31, 31, 31); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">原文提到埃及狩猎者比早期的埃及农民高大。</span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div><div class=\"big-section\">\r\n            <div class=\"q-block normal-q\">\r\n                <div class=\"q-stem\">\r\n                    <span class=\"q-num\">7</span>\r\n                    <div class=\"q-text\"><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><strong>Jay Stock believes that some aspects of early farming life had a damaging effect on people’s health.</strong></span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"opt-list\" style=\"margin:10px 0 10px 25px;\">\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_7\" id=\"opt_7_A\" data-zyz-question=\"q7\" value=\"A\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_7_A\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>A.</strong> TRUE</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_7\" id=\"opt_7_B\" data-zyz-question=\"q7\" value=\"B\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_7_B\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>B.</strong> FALSE</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_7\" id=\"opt_7_C\" data-zyz-question=\"q7\" value=\"C\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_7_C\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>C.</strong> NOT GIVEN</label>\r\n        </div></div>\r\n                <button class=\"btn-toggle\">显示解析</button>\r\n                <div class=\"ans-box\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-row\"><strong>正确答案：</strong> A. TRUE</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"analysis\"><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Q</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">7</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"> TRUE</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">定位关键词：</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">people’s health</p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">原文：</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">E段</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">, “</span>He blames farming for introducing a sedentary lifestyle and the proximity of animals and shared water resources for the spread of infectious diseases.<span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">”</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"> </span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">解析：</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(31, 31, 31); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">原文提到Jay Stock认为早期农业生活改变了一部分人类生活习惯，带来了负面影响。</span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div><div class=\"big-section\">\r\n            <div class=\"q-block normal-q\">\r\n                <div class=\"q-stem\">\r\n                    <span class=\"q-num\">8</span>\r\n                    <div class=\"q-text\"><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><strong>Jared Diamond maintains that farming resulted in social inequality.</strong></span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"opt-list\" style=\"margin:10px 0 10px 25px;\">\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_8\" id=\"opt_8_A\" data-zyz-question=\"q8\" value=\"A\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_8_A\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>A.</strong> TRUE</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_8\" id=\"opt_8_B\" data-zyz-question=\"q8\" value=\"B\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_8_B\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>B.</strong> FALSE</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_8\" id=\"opt_8_C\" data-zyz-question=\"q8\" value=\"C\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_8_C\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>C.</strong> NOT GIVEN</label>\r\n        </div></div>\r\n                <button class=\"btn-toggle\">显示解析</button>\r\n                <div class=\"ans-box\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-row\"><strong>正确答案：</strong> A. TRUE</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"analysis\"><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Q</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">8</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"> TRUE</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">定位关键词：</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(31, 31, 31); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Jared Diam</span>ond，social inequality</p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">原文：</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">E段</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">, “</span>Jared Diamond, in his 1997 book Guns, Germs and Steel, also claims that farming was a retrograde step.<span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">”</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"> </span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">解析：</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(31, 31, 31); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">原文提到Jared Diamond在他的书中声称农业是一种倒退。</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(31, 31, 31); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(31, 31, 31); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">同义替换：</span></p><p>social inequality=<span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"> a retrograde step</span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div><div class=\"big-section\">\r\n            <div class=\"q-block normal-q\">\r\n                <div class=\"q-stem\">\r\n                    <span class=\"q-num\">9</span>\r\n                    <div class=\"q-text\"><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><strong>Modern farming techniques involve a greater reliance on machinery.</strong></span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"opt-list\" style=\"margin:10px 0 10px 25px;\">\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_9\" id=\"opt_9_A\" data-zyz-question=\"q9\" value=\"A\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_9_A\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>A.</strong> TRUE</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_9\" id=\"opt_9_B\" data-zyz-question=\"q9\" value=\"B\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_9_B\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>B.</strong> FALSE</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_9\" id=\"opt_9_C\" data-zyz-question=\"q9\" value=\"C\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_9_C\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>C.</strong> NOT GIVEN</label>\r\n        </div></div>\r\n                <button class=\"btn-toggle\">显示解析</button>\r\n                <div class=\"ans-box\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-row\"><strong>正确答案：</strong> C. NOT GIVEN</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"analysis\"><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Q</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">9</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"> NOT GIVEN</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"> </span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">解析：</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(31, 31, 31); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">原文仅提到现代技术发展使植物的产量提高，并没有提及对机械的依赖。</span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div><div class=\"big-section\">\r\n            <div class=\"q-block normal-q\">\r\n                <div class=\"q-stem\">\r\n                    <span class=\"q-num\">10</span>\r\n                    <div class=\"q-text\"><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><strong>Wild plants can produce more food than equivalent cultivated plants.</strong></span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"opt-list\" style=\"margin:10px 0 10px 25px;\">\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_10\" id=\"opt_10_A\" data-zyz-question=\"q10\" value=\"A\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_10_A\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>A.</strong> TRUE</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_10\" id=\"opt_10_B\" data-zyz-question=\"q10\" value=\"B\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_10_B\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>B.</strong> FALSE</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_10\" id=\"opt_10_C\" data-zyz-question=\"q10\" value=\"C\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_10_C\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>C.</strong> NOT GIVEN</label>\r\n        </div></div>\r\n                <button class=\"btn-toggle\">显示解析</button>\r\n                <div class=\"ans-box\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-row\"><strong>正确答案：</strong> B. FALSE</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"analysis\"><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Q</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">10</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"> FALSE</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">定位关键词：</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">Wild plants</p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">原文：</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">G段</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">, “</span>Over history, by planting selected seeds and improving techniques, farmers have boosted the ability of plants to yield food far above that of their wild counterparts.<span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">”</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"> </span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">解析：</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(31, 31, 31); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">原文在历史上，农民通过种植精选种子和改进技术提高了作物的产量，远远超过了野生作物。</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(31, 31, 31); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(31, 31, 31); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">同义词替换：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">wild counterparts=wild plants</span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div><div class=\"big-section\">\r\n            <div class=\"q-block normal-q\">\r\n                <div class=\"q-stem\">\r\n                    <span class=\"q-num\">11</span>\r\n                    <div class=\"q-text\"><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><strong>Experts believe it will be very difficult to double food production over the next 20 years.</strong></span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"opt-list\" style=\"margin:10px 0 10px 25px;\">\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_11\" id=\"opt_11_A\" data-zyz-question=\"q11\" value=\"A\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_11_A\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>A.</strong> TRUE</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_11\" id=\"opt_11_B\" data-zyz-question=\"q11\" value=\"B\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_11_B\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>B.</strong> FALSE</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_11\" id=\"opt_11_C\" data-zyz-question=\"q11\" value=\"C\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_11_C\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>C.</strong> NOT GIVEN</label>\r\n        </div></div>\r\n                <button class=\"btn-toggle\">显示解析</button>\r\n                <div class=\"ans-box\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-row\"><strong>正确答案：</strong> B. FALSE</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"analysis\"><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Q</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">11</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"> FALSE</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">定位关键词：</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">double food production</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">原文：</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">H段</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">, “</span>Experts consider it entirely realistic to talk of doubling world food production over the next two decades, which is an incredible testament to farming.<span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">”</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"> </span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">解析：</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(31, 31, 31); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">原文提到专家们认为在未来20年内世界粮食产量翻一番是完全现实的。</span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div><div class=\"big-section\">\r\n            <div class=\"q-block normal-q\">\r\n                <div class=\"q-stem\">\r\n                    <span class=\"q-num\">12</span>\r\n                    <div class=\"q-text\"><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><strong>More maize is now eaten by animals than by people.</strong></span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"opt-list\" style=\"margin:10px 0 10px 25px;\">\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_12\" id=\"opt_12_A\" data-zyz-question=\"q12\" value=\"A\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_12_A\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>A.</strong> TRUE</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_12\" id=\"opt_12_B\" data-zyz-question=\"q12\" value=\"B\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_12_B\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>B.</strong> FALSE</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_12\" id=\"opt_12_C\" data-zyz-question=\"q12\" value=\"C\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_12_C\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>C.</strong> NOT GIVEN</label>\r\n        </div></div>\r\n                <button class=\"btn-toggle\">显示解析</button>\r\n                <div class=\"ans-box\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-row\"><strong>正确答案：</strong> A. TRUE</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"analysis\"><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Q</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">12</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"> TRUE</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">定位关键词：</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">animals</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(31, 31, 31); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">原文：</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">H段</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">, “</span>Farmers are already producing enough to feed more than 6 billion people, not to mention a vast quantity of livestock (70% of the world’s maize crop is fed to animals).<span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">”</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"> </span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">解析：</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(31, 31, 31); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">原文提到世界上70%的玉米作物是用来喂养动物的。</span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div><div class=\"big-section\">\r\n            <div class=\"q-block normal-q\">\r\n                <div class=\"q-stem\">\r\n                    <span class=\"q-num\">13</span>\r\n                    <div class=\"q-text\"><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><strong>The UN is confident that it can reach its food production goals.</strong></span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"opt-list\" style=\"margin:10px 0 10px 25px;\">\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_13\" id=\"opt_13_A\" data-zyz-question=\"q13\" value=\"A\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_13_A\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>A.</strong> TRUE</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_13\" id=\"opt_13_B\" data-zyz-question=\"q13\" value=\"B\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_13_B\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>B.</strong> FALSE</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_13\" id=\"opt_13_C\" data-zyz-question=\"q13\" value=\"C\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_13_C\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>C.</strong> NOT GIVEN</label>\r\n        </div></div>\r\n                <button class=\"btn-toggle\">显示解析</button>\r\n                <div class=\"ans-box\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-row\"><strong>正确答案：</strong> C. NOT GIVEN</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"analysis\"><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Q</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">13</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"> NOT GIVEN</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"> </span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">解析：</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(31, 31, 31); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">原文仅提到2030年联合国的目标实现带来的结果，并未提及其是否有信心达成目标。</span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div>",
